    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of tall Brazilian hardwood tree, growing to 40 meters in height. Timber was formerly used for making houses in Brazil, but the species is now threatened with extinction.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
